# Tau Lang

# Specification

## Variable

```
var v: int8 = 7;
```

## Pointer

```
ptr v: int8* = &a;
```

## Function

```
fun f(x: int8): int8 {
    return x;
};
```

## For

## Iff

```
iff (A != B) {
    return 0;
}
```

## Structure

```
str s {
    v1: int8,
    v2: flt8
};
```

## Module resolution

Define a module:
```
mod m;

fun f(x: int8): int8 {
    return x;
}

y = f(3);
```

Require a module:
```
req r;
```
